title: Medical Coverage Assistance Program for Working Individuals with Disabilities
subject: subject index

abstracts.abstract: Medical Coverage Assistance Program for Working Individuals with Disabilities;  Requires AHCA to implement & administer Medicaid buy-in program for specified working individuals with disabilities; provides requirements for program; requires agency to seek by specified date federal approval through Medicaid waiver or state plan amendment to implement program; requires agency to implement & administer program upon receiving federal approval.
